addressed by commit 4bca2a8, under which NCCs can be specified as analytic functions of z, or by array-parameters defined over the z-basis grid. \n\nAdditional options, such as lower bounds on coefficients to include, the ability to use fields, etc., may prove useful.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This has been largely addressed by commit <a href=\"#!/dedalus-project/dedalus/commits/4bca2a8\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">4bca2a8</a>, under which NCCs can be specified as analytic functions of z, or by array-parameters defined over the z-basis grid. </p>\n<p>Additional options, such as lower bounds on coefficients to include, the ability to use fields, etc., may prove useful.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-02-07T03:12:30.626368+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Keaton Burns", "uuid": "{3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279/40f33f99-2b75-4a17-a8c2-07c8d74c7480/128"}}, "nickname": "kburns", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 8125830}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/6/comments/15939050.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/6#comment-15939050"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/6.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 6, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}ts=2009435"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "dedalus", "ful